<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on yutian's blog</title><link>https://yutianovo.github.com/post/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on yutian's blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yutianovo.github.com/post/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用Obsdian写文章并通过脚本发布到Hugo测试</title><link>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8obsdian%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%B9%B6%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%88%B0hugo%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8obsdian%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%B9%B6%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%88%B0hugo%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/</guid><description>&lt;p>参考视频：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dnE7c0ELEH8&lt;br>
参考文章：https://blog.networkchuck.com/posts/my-insane-blog-pipeline/&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://yutianovo.github.com/images/Pasted%20image%2020241130212031.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="Image Description"
>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hugo 博客搭建时的问题</title><link>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/hugo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:48:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/hugo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="不会自动换行">不会自动换行
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>打开 hugo 博客的文件夹，全局搜索 goldmark&lt;br>
如果是 toml 格式，就改为下面的内容&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">goldmark&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">renderer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">unsafe&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">hardwraps&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>yaml 格式&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">markup&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">goldmark&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">renderer&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">hardWraps&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="chrome-extension://mapjgeachilmcbbokkgcbgpbakaaeehi/assets/check.svg"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Clash Verge 将订阅中的代理地址作为单个端口开放</title><link>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/clash-verge-%E5%B0%86%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE/</link><pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:24:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yutianovo.github.com/p/clash-verge-%E5%B0%86%E8%AE%A2%E9%98%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AA%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE/</guid><description>&lt;p>来到 Profile 选中订阅地址，点击右键选择 Open File 或者 Edit File&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://yutianovo.github.com/images/Pasted%20image%2020241130213818.png"
loading="lazy"
alt="Image Description"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在 proxies 上方新增如下内容&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">19
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">listeners&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">mixed-in&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">mixed&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">27891&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">listen&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">127.0.0.1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">proxies 中的 name 字段 - 美国节点&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">users&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">admin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">password &lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">socks-in&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">socks&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">27892&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">listen&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">127.0.0.1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">proxies 中的 name 字段 - 新加坡节点&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">http-in&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">http&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">27893&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">listen&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">127.0.0.1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">proxies 中的 name 字段 - 香港节点&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>以下配置将在本地启动一个节点，归属为香港，并开放同时支持 HTTP 和 SOCKS 协议的端口 &lt;code>17891&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">port: &lt;span class="m">7890&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">socks-port: &lt;span class="m">7891&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">allow-lan: &lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mode: Rule
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">log-level: info
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">external-controller: 127.0.0.1:9090
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">listeners:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - name: mixed-in
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> type: mixed
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> port: &lt;span class="m">27891&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> listen: 127.0.0.1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> proxy: &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;🇭🇰 港hk&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">proxies:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - &lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>name: 🇭🇰 港hk, server: ...&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>snip&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>... true&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>完成后选择重启应用，当订阅更新时，配置将消失。&lt;/p>
